data.description: Lovely 2bd/2ba SOLAR home in the popular Seasons RV Village subdivisions (with no HOA's!).  This well maintained home has unobstructed desert views and endless sunsets to the west with cozy entertainment spaces.  On the interior you'll love the the kitchen and it's large island which is adjacent to a spacious dining and living room. The outdoor living spaces feature a concrete pad and pergola, a 10 X 20 insulated framed workshop, 20' automatic metal gate, & RV hookup with RV parking. You will love!
